{"tid":1883723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"註冊國際救援護士 你問我答","createTime":"2020-02-17T07:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T05:42:00.000Z","uid":349496,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"11715f2a42ee125689ed086f272eb2ad22cb4863","tid":1883723,"uid":349496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:10:23.000Z","msg":"Hello大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我係梁姑娘啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，係一個註冊護士同埋有多年國際救援護士經驗，同時擁有五個保險牌照及多年保險索償經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。熟悉政府及私家醫院運作之餘，都協助左好多保險從業員及企業員工使用保險，所以開個你問我答，睇下大家對邊類問題有興趣。<br />\n<br />\n我開左youtube同facebook channel,，如果有邊類問題比較多人問，我會係 channel再深入講解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以多按like 同訂閱，大約幾日就會更新下影片，分享下醫療，健康衛生既知識<br />\n<br />\nYoutube: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCq8pcU1EfvR6jYpvFpkQdMQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCq8pcU1EfvR6jYpvFpkQdMQ&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=43bce8be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCq8pcU1EfvR6jYpvFpkQdMQ</a><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"http://fb.me/nurseleung\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Fnurseleung&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=c90d062d\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.me/nurseleung</a><br />\n<br />\n如果有時唔知自己應該睇咩專科，或者想要多一個醫療建議，都可以問喔"},{"pid":"2b0f9df3e2e992f3150b0ec279aa93ab88588b2f","tid":1883723,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:11:29.000Z","msg":"幾歲？"},{"pid":"b6440db5b4dab1fd2e99aad46f81a98709afd1cb","tid":1883723,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:15:25.000Z","msg":"國際救援同一般註冊護士有咩唔同"},{"pid":"b5ffd49875c6bcaa2b93c07e357ef128dadf75ee","tid":1883723,"uid":349496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b0f9df3e2e992f3150